                P
              
            
            x
          
        
        
        d
        x
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\hat {f}}\left({\tfrac {k}{P}}\right)=\int _{P}f_{P}(x)\cdot e^{-i2\pi {\frac {k}{P}}x}\,dx.}
  When 
  
    
      
        f
        (
        x
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle f(x)}
   has compact support, 
  
    
      
        
          f
          
            P
          
        
        (
        x
