Invertibility and periodicity
Under suitable conditions on the function 
  
    
      
        f
      
    
    {\displaystyle f}
  , it can be recovered from its Fourier transform 
  
    
      
        
          
            
              f
              ^
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\hat {f}}}
  . Indeed, denoting the Fourier transform operator by 
  
    
      
        
          
