    {\displaystyle {\hat {h}}(\xi )={\overline {{\hat {f}}(\xi )}}{\hat {f}}(\xi )=\left|{\hat {f}}(\xi )\right|^{2}.}

Eigenfunctions
The Fourier transform is a linear transform which has eigenfunctions obeying 
  
    
      
        
          
