        (
        ξ
        )
      
    
    {\displaystyle {\hat {f}}(\xi )=F_{0}(|\xi |)P(\xi )}
  where

  
    
      
        
          F
          
            0
          
        
        (
        r
        )
        =
        2
        π
        
          i
          
